      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"the data overwhelmingly shows\" is a huge claim. isn't it true that some economists argue that union monopolies can lead to inefficiencies or even prevent new businesses from starting? it seems like there's a legitimate debate about the trade-offs here, not just one side being right and the other a \"myth\".",
